              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The polarimeter is used in detection.",
                " Left and right scattering from the 5 g/cm2 thick",
                " carbon scatterer was detected in double coincidence",
                " telescopes divided into an inner and an outer angular",
                " channel and consisting of the scintillators.",
                "The beam was monitored by a scintillator telescope",
                " directed towards the target."
